"To take advantage of the latest WordPress has to offer, our WordPress "
"Onboarding to setup your website requires the latest version of WordPress."
msgstr ""
"Um die Vorteile der neuesten WordPress hat zu bieten, unsere WordPress-"
"Onboarding, um Ihre Website einzurichten erfordert die neueste Version von "
"WordPress."

